  ],
  "subject": [],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "",
      "abstract": "Provides that companion animals, as sentient beings, shall be considered victims of animal cruelty crimes, including but not limited to all offenses as defined in article twenty-six of the agriculture and markets law, and shall be treated as such in a court of law."
    }
